Synthetic ETFs Need Caution, EU’s Lueder Says

-- B y   B e n   M o s h i n s k y
-- 
2011-09-20T09:27:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/synthetic-etfs-need-caution-eu-s-lueder-says.html
European regulators “have to take
a critical and careful view” of so-called synthetic exchange
traded funds, Tilman Lueder, a European Commission official,
said in a speech in  London  today.  “You’re gaining exposure to assets via derivative
transactions,” Lueder said. “There’s something strange about
this, why don’t you buy the assets?”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Moshinsky in Brussels at 
 bmoshinsky@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
